### Corpse Tab

This function monitors if a corpse has spawned on your server and sends you a Discord notification when it does.

**How to configure:**

1. In the Corpse tab, paste your Discord Webhook link in the indicated field.
2. Enter your Discord User ID to be mentioned in the message (optional).
3. Click "Select area" and mark the region of the screen where the corpse spawn notification (IT APPEARS AGAIN) appears in-game.
4. Activate the detector with the Activate button.

**How to create a Discord Webhook:**
1. Open the Discord channel settings.
2. Go to Integrations → Webhooks → New Webhook.
3. Copy the link and paste it into JesterHub.

