## ⚙️ Settings and Profiles

Click the gear icon (⚙️) at the top of the macro to open the settings.

**What you can change:**

- Language: Portuguese or English.

**Profiles (saving settings):**

JesterHub has 3 profile slots. Each profile saves all your settings — sensitivity, speed, blocked keys, hotkeys, and more.

- Save: Click the slot number to save the current profile.
- Load: Click a previously saved slot to load the settings.

