## 🔔 Notifications and Hotkeys

JesterHub shows notifications in the corner of the screen when you activate or deactivate a function — this is especially useful when the macro is minimized.

| Key | Function |
|---|---|
| F6 | Toggle Minigame On/Off |
| F7 | Toggle Auto Fish On/Off |

