## ❓ Common Issues

The macro doesn't detect the letter / shows "Not defined"
→ Redefine the detection area. Select the area very tightly around the white letter inside the circle.

Auto Fish is pulling at the wrong time / detecting non-bite sounds
→ Move the Sensitivity slider to the right (more strict). If the problem persists, try recalibrating the sound in a quieter environment in-game.

Auto Fish is missing fish / not detecting the bite
→ Check if the game volume is high enough. Move the Sensitivity slider to the left. Try recalibrating with a clearer bite sound.

The macro is too slow to press the key in the minigame
→ Reduce the Speed in the Minigame tab (lower value = faster). 0ms is the fastest possible.

My key isn't working
→ The HWID changes if you switch computers or reinstall Windows. Please contact me.

